                            p.lead.mb-0 Do you know that some italian villages are being sold for just 1 euro?
                    .col-lg-4
                        .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0.mb-lg-3
                            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
                                i.bi-house-check-fill.m-auto.text-primary
